---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 31
  - Title: Chuang-tse
    Chapter: 22
By: Zhuang-Zi
Tags:
  - Creation=Inexhaustibility of the Creator
  - Union-Identity=Holiness-Universal Man=Universal Man
---
Unfathomable as the sea, wondrously ending only to begin again, informing
all creation without being exhausted, the Tao of the perfect man is
spontaneous in its operation.
